      "content": "It's true, the things that once mattered are gone, but that doesn't mean you can't find a new purpose. You can still make a difference, even if it's not in the same way as before. Maybe it's time to start fresh, to create a new version of yourself that can bring joy and meaning to your life. There's always a chance for redemption, even if it feels impossible right now. Don't give up on yourself just yet.",
      "source": "target",
